title: Kangana Ranaut Pulls A Catwoman For The Screening Of Rangoon
text:
facebook 357 SHARES 
In her upcoming movie, Rangoon , Kangana Ranaut is seen doing a lot of stunts. From a duel with Saif Ali Khan, to jumping on the top of a train, she is indeed Toofan ki beti . 
For the screening of the movie, yesterday, Kangana dressed in a fierce black ensemble, much like Catwoman, or so we feel! The actress wore a striped pantsuit, with a corset like vest, that stole the show. The bold red lips, nude heels, and a touch of those nerdy glasses was enough to knock us off our feet.
